description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 40, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 200, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, Box for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10405-19490-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [200 Votes, Top 5% Score]
